5 Red Lobster is  consistently excellent. The Biscuits may be a draw for some ,(altho I can only eat one myself).  I go back over and over because of the great staff, the impeccable Long Island Iced Teas and the always Hot Steamy Perfect  FRESH Lobster. Our Madison Red Lobster aims to please like no other chain in town. The menu is extensive and never disappointing. I am thrilled to have them here. Worth the time and money, every visit.
